---
const credentials = [
  'Three graduate degrees — international development & sociology',
  'Only Pakistani org selected for AI Opportunity Fund: Asia-Pacific',
  'Funded by AVPN, Google.org, ISOC & Asian Development Bank',
  'Founded in Lasbela — built for the world',
  'Founder of five live digital platforms across two continents',
];
---

<section class="story section" id="story">
  <div class="story__inner container">
    <div class="story__left">
      <div class="story__left-sticky">
        <span class="eyebrow reveal">Story</span>
        <h2 class="story__heading reveal">
          The mission came first.<br />
          <em>The tech followed.</em>
        </h2>
        <ul class="story__credentials reveal">
          {credentials.map((item) => (
            <li class="story__credential">
              <span class="story__credential-mark" aria-hidden="true">&#9670;</span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story__right">
      <div class="story__narrative">
        <p class="story__paragraph story__paragraph--dropcap reveal">
          I came to AI through development work — not the other way around. After years studying how communities are shaped by systems of power and exclusion, I watched artificial intelligence become the most consequential of those systems. The question underneath all of my work has always been the same: who gets left out?
        </p>

        <p class="story__paragraph reveal">
          Urdu AI started from that gap — and grew into Pakistan&rsquo;s leading AI literacy platform, now reaching over one million people through social media, a weekly newsletter, a mobile app, and workshops across the country. The largest Urdu-language AI education community in the world, built without a venture round and without corporate backing.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="story__pullquote reveal">
          <p>220 million people speak Urdu. Almost none of the world&rsquo;s AI education reaches them. So I built the infrastructure to change that.</p>
        </blockquote>

        <p class="story__paragraph reveal">
          Then came PakSpeed — because you cannot talk about digital inclusion without honest data on who actually has connectivity and who doesn&rsquo;t. In its first seven days, Pakistan&rsquo;s first community-owned internet speed monitoring network logged over 15,000 tests. Real data. Real accountability. Built for the people it measures.
        </p>

        <p class="story__paragraph reveal">
          WANG and its innovation lab WALI have been working on the ground for years — girls&rsquo; education, flood rehabilitation housing, rural digital literacy, and youth leadership in communities where the digital divide is not a statistic but a daily reality. Trusted and funded by Internet Society, AVPN, and Google.
        </p>

        <p class="story__paragraph story__paragraph--closing reveal">
          Different platforms. Different communities. One conviction: AI should belong to everyone who needs it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .story__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 35% 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .story__left-sticky {
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  .story__heading em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .story__credentials {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .story__credential {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .story__credential-mark {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .story__narrative {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .story__paragraph {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.92;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .story__paragraph--dropcap::first-letter {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    float: left;
    line-height: 0.8;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  .story__paragraph--closing {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .story__pullquote {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    background: rgba(184, 145, 60, 0.06);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .story__pullquote p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .story__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .story__left-sticky {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
